Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.99,0:02:22.91,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(180,110)}Valley of the Welling Tides
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! That guy came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he wasn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your leg injury had weakened you \Nand caused you to pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband found you and carried you \Nback to our home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank him for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to till our land on the mountain slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't be back until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to rush me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you something to fill you up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I've entered paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold yourself back. Eat your fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that a green field of rice I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, couldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the middle of winter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that the sound of a hoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is someone outside tilling at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your leg better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your husband hasn't returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he came back around dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but he left again right after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the fields out back at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't imagine it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it possible spring came without my realizing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, don't tell me I'm actually still out there \Nfreezing to death and this is all just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you probably shouldn't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had a rough time, so feel free to rest here as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, these rice paddies are very impressive, especially given the time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just work on them nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He gives off a sweet scent...{uh oh}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you didn't do anything special?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can work day and night without feeling a bit of fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider these rice paddies as the fruits of my labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was this scent, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, I made tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll take a break, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the husband's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I take it that his mother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed away a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost her about a year after she gave birth to your son, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the circumstances of her death were strange, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be a mushi-shi, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy for me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believe your son may be under the influence of mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there other details you'd care to share with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If my hunch is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the lives of both your son and your daughter-in-law are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have you saying anything untoward to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to repay our kindness by doing us harm, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ever tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't finish your vegetables again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to become tough like your dad, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better clean your plate, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it. Attaboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, can I have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look who's suddenly eager!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're a mushi-shi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this important thing you have to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get more rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone far beyond your body's natural limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for your concern, but I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been this way for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely get a good night's rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My body gets restless when I try to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back out in the fields before I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you're likely unaware of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a mushi that's responsible for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. It's my free will that's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, this place was just a desolate, empty valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've toiled for years to transform it into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked day and night, day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who made the valley into what it is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a better life for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure they'd never suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this came from what {\i1}I{\i0} wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still want it if you knew it was built on the sacrifice of your mother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you not to say anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in his own best interests to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere any further \Nwith this family,{Comma for dramatic emphasis} or this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi, are you going to \Ntill the fields on the slopes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want another paddy ready to go by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What you heard earlier today... Is it bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After she gave birth to me, \Nshe grew weaker and died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who took Mom from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why I have to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for stepping over the line earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mushi purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Should there come a time when you feel it's necessary, feel free to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right before.{Technically, this should be a colon, but meh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right \Nto take away this valley's prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come inside soo—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should stay and rest awhile, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I just got careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, you're working too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a seat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you all mind giving us some privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to take this tale to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now, Houichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, you're still unable to produce milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because I haven't been able to feed you properly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the valley was flush with new immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so everyone was barely scraping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could afford to share their milk with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were at our wits' end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't find Houichi some milk soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sweet smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That pond is pure white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You suckled on it with single-minded intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the following day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo finally started producing milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that white water was some kind of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never found that white pond again, no matter how much we searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank your mother's milk and grew steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, almost as if in counter to your growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo's health deteriorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face looks really pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm producing a lot of milk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... breast milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sought out doctors far and wide for {help or even just }answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but not one of them believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, around the time you were to be weaned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ever tell him about my illness... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to be happy, \Nso he mustn't know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've liked to have watched over him, \Nbut I don't think I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be all right, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me, Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet even with her last breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother wished only for your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So my body grew this strong \Nbecause I suckled the blood of my own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What caused you to do that \Nwas a Chishio, or "Milk Tide" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chishio is a parasite \Nthat seeks out a newborn to be its host{Timing: Join if you'd like. I'd prefer it, but I didn't check the audio length or the line length.}{i'd like to, but 126 characters...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then turns the bodily fluids of the newborn's mother into milk for its own nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As the host matures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts to exude a particular scent \Nthat promotes the growth of nearby plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chishio then pushes its host \Nto neglect sleep and keep eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,focusing on building its own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once its host collapses from exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Chishio leaves its host \Nand ensnares yet another infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So these rice paddies were all thanks to the mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who actually cultivated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If or when you decide to take the mushi purge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just let your dad know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot give up this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer an infant who needs someone to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I, too, have a family I must protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it means I must use \Nthe same power that killed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mom. I only ever bring you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, he's become a fine father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Milk turns to blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nourishes the earth, and then returns to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the earth is imbued with a living, welling tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the valley came to endure \Nthe first of several harsh winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. We're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even now, the valley \Nechoes with laughter and joy.
